===National Invitation Tournament===
{{mainarticle|2010 National Invitation Tournament}}
The Big Ten earned two postseason [[National Invitation Tournament]] invitations.  Its teams combined for 2 wins and 2 losses, with Illinois earning both wins.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nit.org/history/nit-postseason-results-2010s.html|title=Tournament Results (2010's)|accessdate=2010-08-11|publisher=[[CBS Interactive]]}}</ref>
